Our Western Yoke Triple Stitched Cotton Twill Welding Shirts are manufactured with the utmost quality. Featuring organic Peruvian cotton and a standard fit, the shirts are designed to provide maximum comfort and durability. With triple hand-stitched construction, these work shirts are sure to last.

  • Non Fire-Retardant (For Certified FR Shirts Click Here)
  • Machine Washable, 8 Ounce, 100% Cotton Twill
  • Two Chest Pockets with Flaps and Snap Closures
  • Triple-Snap Cuffs with Extended Plackets
  • Left-Pocket Flap with Pencil Opening
  • Pearl-Colored Snaps throughout
  • Relaxed Fit with Spread Collar
  • Front and Back Western-Shaped Yokes
  • Strong Triple-Stitched Over Every Seam
  • Takes Starch Really Well

Great quality but big gap between sizes

Overall build quality is amazing and the shape is nice. It doesn’t flare out wide like the wrangler pearl snaps. There’s a pretty big gap between sizes and I’m still trying to find which one works for me. The large is a little snug and the XL was falling off of me and with it being 100% cotton I’m a little worried about it shrinking in the wash. But once I decide which size works best I’ll be buying more for sure.
